//000000000020a:4:{i:0;a:14:{s:2:"id";s:2:"39";s:5:"title";s:30:"温哥华插班学习春节游";s:7:"content";s:4588:"<p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">项目介绍：</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 115%;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在北美第一留学平台虎妈之家的专业指导和计划下，带着孩子飞往加拿大温哥华，展开一次梦想中的全家游学！</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 115%;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">孩子不仅能插班进当地学校读书，还能受到家长全身心的陪伴；学习之余，全家可以在宜人的风景中放松自我，体味当地风土人情，尽享加拿大城市生活的繁华舒适！</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">留学时间：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2016</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">31</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">日至</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;"> 2016</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">14</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">日，具体见方案</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">参加人员：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1-7</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年级学生及陪读家长；</span> </strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">留学地点：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加拿大温哥华</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 101px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 19