其中周三</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">8:45AM – 2:00PM</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">课程设置：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">基本课程为英文、数学、科学、音乐、体育、艺术、戏剧、历史、地理、圣经等等。各年级略有不同。</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">签证类型：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="color: red; font-family: 宋体;">旅游签证</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">费用</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">包含：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学习费用：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为期三周的入学学费</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">出国手续：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">帮助办理签证</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">住宿费：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为期三周的住宿费用，原则住<strong>家庭旅馆（</strong></span><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">richmond</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">距离学校车程</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">分钟。可以在家庭旅馆自己做三餐；父母陪孩子一起参加。</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Party</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">费用</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：组办方将组织</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">次新春</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Party,</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">将邀请当地华裔孩子参加</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">留学指导费用：</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;">——行前和落地行程指导；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;">——推荐参与本地选修文体活动，如网球、游泳、攀岩、跆拳道、唱诗班、成人短期英文补习等；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;">——周末家庭出游计划，组办方推荐安排温哥华、维多利亚、惠斯勒、西雅图等多个加拿大、美国著名景点的旅游。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">自费部分：</span></strong></p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">家庭签证费</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（包括留学孩子和陪读家长）。</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">往返机票费用</span></strong>(<span style="font-family: 宋体;">携程成人经济舱价格在</span>6000 – 9000<span style="font-family: 宋体;">人民币左右</span>)<span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">温哥华当地租车费用</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（小型车含基本保险租金低至</span>200<span style="font-family: 宋体;">人民币</span>/<span style="font-family: 宋体;">天起，可以月租更省费用</span>2000<span style="font-family: 宋体;">元起，或者两，三个家庭拼一辆车）。</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">餐饮费用</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（超市里的猪肉、蔬菜大多</span>3-5<span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币一斤，自己做饭开销不大。外出用餐价差很大。麦当劳、外卖中餐等快餐每人</span>6-10<span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币，普通中餐每人</span>8-15<span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币。孩子学校午餐</span>5<span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币一天）</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">课外活动自费选项：</span></strong></p></li></ol><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、高尔夫</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">80--120</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">小时；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、网球</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">60-80</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">小时；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、羽毛球</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">50-60</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">小时；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、冰球</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">80</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">小时；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、智能机器人</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">30</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">小时；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、美国或加拿大数学竞赛</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">50</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">小时；</span></p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">英语口语</span>40<span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span>/<span style="font-family: 宋体;">小时，</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;">8<span style="font-family: 宋体;">、滑雪</span>260<span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span>/<span style="font-family: 宋体;">半天（</span>2<span style="font-family: 宋体;">次包会，教练接送）</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">旅游自费选项：</span></strong></p></li></ol><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、温哥华一日游</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">120</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、维多利亚一日游</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">150</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、惠斯勒一日游</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">150</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、班芙三日游</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">350</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、黄刀北极光三日游</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">500</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币不含机票，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 76px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、美国西雅图三日游</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">400</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加币</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人（需要美国签证）</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">7</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、温哥华岛探险一日游</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">150</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">元</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">天，含轮渡，车辆，午餐：近距离观看野生海狮、海星、水母及大量飞鸟，认识森林各种植物；</span></p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个人消费</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（温哥华机场附件大型奥特莱斯，</span>Downtown<span style="font-family: 宋体;">有繁华的商场。）</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">家长单独房间费用；</span></strong></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">国际医疗保险费用</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></p></li></ol><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">你的准备：</span></strong></p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">签证需要材料：</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学校要求：</span> <span style="font-family: 宋体;">待定</span></p></li></ol><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、自带笔记本电脑用于机器人培训；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">费用支付：</span></strong></p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">付款：</span></strong></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">对此留学项目感兴趣的家庭请先交订金</span>3000<span style="font-family: 宋体;">元签意向合同。订金不退。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">签证办出后签署正式合同，支付后续款项，并选择选修课程（用于提前联系并约定导师）</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;">&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;">&nbsp;</p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">退款：</span></strong></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学校开学前，如因特殊情况临时不能成行，所交费用退回一半。开学后，所有费用恕不退还。</span></p></li></ol><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>";s:10:"view_count";s:2:"34";s:8:"cover_id";s:2:"24";s:8:"issue_id";s:2:"16";s:3:"uid";s:3:"108";s:11:"reply_count";s:1:"0";s:11:"create_time";s:10:"1446966027";s:11:"update_time";s:10:"1447044296";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:3:"url";s:7:"http://";s:4:"user";a:6:{s:2:"id";s:3:"108";s:8:"nickname";s:5:"Randy";s:9:"space_url";s:46:"/index.php?s=/ucenter/index/index/uid/108.html";s:10:"space_link";s:88:"<a ucard=108 target=_blank href=/index.php?s=/ucenter/index/index/uid/108.html>Randy</a>";s:9:"avatar128";s:44:"Uploads/Avatar/108/56401a10a74af_128_128.JPG";s:13:"real_nickname";s:5:"Randy";}s:5:"issue";a:2:{s:2:"id";s:2:"16";s:5:"title";s:9:"插班生";}}i:2;a:14:{s:2:"id";s:2:"41";s:5:"title";s:33:"加拿大环宇学院考察之旅";s:7:"content";s:3320:"<p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">出行时间：</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2016.1.23-2.2</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">报名对象：国内家长及子女</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">出团人数：</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">15-20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</spa